{"tid":650073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[又贏]本港露宿人數創5年新高突破一千人","createTime":"2018-05-02T04:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T06:38:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a8335ae152f417bdd891b90f22119f036edc48","tid":650073,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T04:26:13.000Z","msg":"香港露宿者有上升趨勢，根據社會福利署過往5年的數據，登記在系統內的露宿者人數在17/18年有1127人，較去年924人增逾200人 ，<span style=\"color: red;\">增幅近兩成</span>。當中三個年齡層都有明顯上升，包括30歲至49歲、50歲至69歲及70歲或以上，當中50歲至69歲的露宿者最多，達634人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1408884/org/861ab9c44fc2e0c757279734b6d6d6b0.jpg/2xWn5MG7OZ03afV-DvH62iD8DLGFiCzER-hUEUfoVBE?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1408884%2Forg%2F861ab9c44fc2e0c757279734b6d6d6b0.jpg%2F2xWn5MG7OZ03afV-DvH62iD8DLGFiCzER-hUEUfoVBE%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=b5e8714d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文件中亦有顯示露宿者露宿原因，當中394人因失業以致無力支付租金需要露宿街頭，有177人無法可找到可負擔租金的居所。其他原因分別為剛從醫院/監獄/戒毒所離開未能找到居所、個人選擇及其他原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/184058/%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E9%9C%B2%E5%AE%BF%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%89%B55%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA-394%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%B2%E5%AE%BF%E5%9B%A0%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%9B%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E7%A7%9F%E9%87%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F184058%2F%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%2589%25B55%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258D%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA-394%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259C%25B2%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E4%25BB%2598%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2587%2591&d=nRHBUVZHhqwhhyqBOnRgtLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h